pageContext.claim: “Richard Grenell has done one of the best jobs I've ever seen. I mean, in a short period of time, he exposed them as being corrupt.”
pageContext.analysis: Trump and his allies mischaracterized several documents released by Grenell, a Trump ally who served as acting director of national intelligence. They do not prove that the Obama administration illegally spied or corruptly plotted against Trump, as he claims.
